---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="L'ÉLÉGANCE | Alta Cocina Contemporánea" description="Descubra una experiencia gastronómica única en el corazón de la ciudad.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="Interior del restaurante elegante"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 object-center"
      />
      <!-- Gradient overlay for readability -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-950 via-zinc-950/60 to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-950/80 via-transparent to-zinc-950/80"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center mt-20">
      <span class="block text-gold-400 font-serif tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs md:text-sm mb-6">
        Une Expérience Unique
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-serif mb-8 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-xl font-light">
        L'Art de la<br/><i class="text-gold-400 font-normal">Gastronomie</i>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-300 font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Descubra una sinfonía de sabores en el corazón de la ciudad. Alta cocina elaborada con pasión y los mejores ingredientes de temporada en un ambiente inigualable.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center w-full sm:w-auto">
        <a href="/carta" class="px-10 py-4 bg-gold-400 text-zinc-950 font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-sm hover:bg-gold-500 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          Ver la Carta
        </a>
        <a href="#reservas" class="px-10 py-4 border border-gold-400 text-gold-400 font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-sm hover:bg-gold-400 hover:text-zinc-950 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm bg-zinc-950/30">
          Reservar Mesa
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce">
      <div class="w-[1px] h-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-gold-400 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Experience Section -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-zinc-950 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 border border-gold-500/20 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 z-0"></div>
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550966871-3ed3cdb5ed0c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Chef preparando un plato"
            class="relative z-10 w-full h-[600px] object-cover filter brightness-90 hover:brightness-100 transition-all duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <span class="text-gold-400 font-serif tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm">Nuestra Filosofía</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white font-light leading-tight">
              Tradición culinaria con un toque <i class="text-gold-400 font-normal">vanguardista</i>
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
            En L'ÉLÉGANCE, creemos que cada plato cuenta una historia. Nuestro Chef Ejecutivo combina técnicas clásicas con innovaciones modernas para crear experiencias memorables que deleitan todos los sentidos.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Seleccionamos meticulosamente ingredientes de temporada, trabajando directamente con productores locales para garantizar la frescura y calidad excepcional en cada bocado.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Highlight Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-900 border-y border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="text-gold-400 font-serif tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-4 block">Experiencia</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-white font-light mb-16">Un ambiente diseñado para el disfrute</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border border-gold-400/30 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0 0 12 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white">Arquitectura Íntima</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light text-center leading-relaxed">
            Espacios diseñados para ofrecer privacidad y confort, con una iluminación tenue que invita a la conversación.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border border-gold-400/30 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 0 1 4.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0 1 12 15a9.065 9.065 0 0 0-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8 1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0 1 12 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white">Bodega Exclusiva</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light text-center leading-relaxed">
            Más de 500 referencias de vinos internacionales, cuidadosamente seleccionados por nuestro sumiller.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border border-gold-400/30 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 0 1 1.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 0 0 .475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 0 0-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 0 1-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.562.562 0 0 0-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 0 1-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 0 0-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.562.562 0 0 1 .321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 0 0 .475-.345L11.48 3.5Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white">Servicio Impecable</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light text-center leading-relaxed">
            Un equipo dedicado a anticipar sus necesidades y asegurar que cada detalle sea absolutamente perfecto.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reservation Section -->
  <section id="reservas" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-zinc-950 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/80"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="block text-gold-400 font-serif tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-6">Asegure su mesa</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white font-light mb-8">Haga su reserva</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-300 font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Le invitamos a realizar su reserva con antelación. Para mesas de más de 6 personas o eventos privados, por favor contáctenos directamente.
      </p>

      <form class="bg-zinc-900/80 backdrop-blur-md p-8 md:p-12 border border-zinc-800 text-left max-w-3xl mx-auto shadow-2xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div>
            <label for="date" class="block text-sm font-light text-zinc-400 mb-2 tracking-wide uppercase">Fecha</label>
            <input type="date" id="date" class="w-full bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-700 pb-2 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-gold-400 transition-colors font-light color-scheme-dark" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="time" class="block text-sm font-light text-zinc-400 mb-2 tracking-wide uppercase">Hora</label>
            <select id="time" class="w-full bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-700 pb-2 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-gold-400 transition-colors font-light appearance-none">
              <option value="">Seleccione una hora</option>
              <option value="13:30">13:30</option>
              <option value="14:00">14:00</option>
              <option value="14:30">14:30</option>
              <option value="20:30">20:30</option>
              <option value="21:00">21:00</option>
              <option value="21:30">21:30</option>
              <option value="22:00">22:00</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="guests" class="block text-sm font-light text-zinc-400 mb-2 tracking-wide uppercase">Personas</label>
            <select id="guests" class="w-full bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-700 pb-2 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-gold-400 transition-colors font-light appearance-none">
              <option value="2">2 Personas</option>
              <option value="3">3 Personas</option>
              <option value="4">4 Personas</option>
              <option value="5">5 Personas</option>
              <option value="6">6 Personas</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-light text-zinc-400 mb-2 tracking-wide uppercase">Nombre</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Su nombre completo" class="w-full bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-700 pb-2 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-gold-400 transition-colors font-light" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="w-full py-4 bg-gold-400 text-zinc-950 font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-sm hover:bg-gold-500 transition-colors duration-300">
          Solicitar Reserva
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
